               was sent by the remoote port.
   echostr   - pointer to a string of textthat will be displayed on the remote
               user's port.
   cluster - the CnmpCluster that was initialized and returned by @{"InitCNMP()" Link InitCNMP()}

@{b}   RESULT@{ub}
